                <div class="col-3 active"><img src="/Image/Main/img-sales5.jpg" /></div>
                <div class="col-3"><img src="/Image/Main/img-sales2.jpeg" /></div>
                <div class="col-3"><img src="/Image/Main/img-sales7.jpg" /></div>
                <div class="col-3"><img src="/Image/Main/img-sales8.jpg" /></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="main-info-p col-12 col-lg-7 mt-3 mt-lg-0 pr-sm-4 pl-sm-4 pr-lg-2 pl-lg-2">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-block">
                    <p class="main-info-title text-oneline-overhidden"><span class="my-title-12">旺仔牛奶</span></p>
                    <p class="main-info-description card-text text-oneline-overhidden">旺仔牛奶是一种营养牛奶饮品，对小孩子的成长具有促进作用，有增食欲、促睡眠、祛疲劳等多项保健功能。是一种适合小孩子饮用的营养品。</p>
                    <div class="main-info-description-all"> 旺仔牛奶是一种营养牛奶饮品，对小孩子的成长具有促进作用，有增食欲、促睡眠、祛疲劳等多项保健功能。是一种适合小孩子饮用的营养品。</div>
                    <!--价格-->
                    <div class="main-info-price">
                        <span>价格：</span><span class="red-price">￥99</span>
                    </div>
                    <!--运费-->
                    <div class="main-info-freight">
                        <span>运费：杭州&nbsp;至&nbsp;</span><span class="arrive-city">龙泉&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;快递：0.00</span>
                    </div>
                    <!--销售信息-->
                    <div class="main-info-saleinfo row text-center">
                        <div class="col-6 text-oneline-overhidden">月销量&nbsp;<span>99</span></div>
                        <div class="col-6 text-oneline-overhidden">累计评价&nbsp;<span>99</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <!--商品规格与数量-->
                    <div class="main-info-style">
                        <div class="main-info-size">
                            <div>规格</div>
                            <div class="active">1m</div>
                            <div>2m</div>
                            <div>3m</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="main-info-color">
                            <div>颜色分类</div>
                            <div class="active">白色</div>
                            <div>黑色</div>
                            <div>蓝色</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="main-info-count">
                            <div>数量</div>
                            <div class="input-group mr-1" style="width: 7rem;"><input class="form-control" type="number" value="1" /><div class="input-group-addon">件</div></div>
                            <div class="ml-3">库存 100件</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!--按钮组-->
                    <div class="main-info-btngroup row m-0 text-center justify-content-around">
                        <div class="col-5 btn btn-info">立即购买</div>
                        <div class="col-5 btn btn-info">加入购物车</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
